<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 06:14:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来已完成4000万次电池更换</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-nio-has-completed-40-million-battery-swaps-so-far-2024-03-14/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车首席执行官李斌周四表示，迄今为止已完成 4000 万次电池更换。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 05:55:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-maker-nio-has-completed-40-million-battery-swaps-so-far-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲投资者关注下一轮美国数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-14/</link><description>Rae Wee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 05:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，各国正在接近数字货币，但美国落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/countries-closing-digital-currencies-us-lagging-study-shows-2024-03-14/</link><description>周四一项备受关注的研究显示，占全球经济总量 98% 的 134 个国家目前正在探索其货币的数字版本，其中一半以上处于高级开发、试点或启动阶段。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 04:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/countries-closing-digital-currencies-us-lagging-study-shows-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>人力资源部称，中国任命陈晓东为外交部副部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-appoints-chen-xiaodong-vice-foreign-minister-says-human-resources-ministry-2024-03-14/</link><description>人力资源部周四在一份声明中表示，中国任命陈晓东为外交部副部长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-appoints-chen-xiaodong-vice-foreign-minister-says-human-resources-ministry-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市持稳；日经指数因日本央行的关键押注而受损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-14/</link><description>亚洲股市周四维持在七个月高位附近，但主要横盘整理，因为投资者等待新的催化剂，这将进一步明确全球利率宽松周期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>经中国批准，日本建投公司将于 3 月 19 日开始对 JSR 进行要约收购 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-jic-start-tender-offer-jsr-march-19-after-chinese-approval-bloomberg-news-2024-03-14/</link><description>据彭博社周四报道，日本国家投资公司（JIC）在获得中国监管机构批准后，将于 3 月 19 日开始对芯片材料制造商 JSR Corp 的股票进行要约收购。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-jic-start-tender-offer-jsr-march-19-after-chinese-approval-bloomberg-news-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>尽管地区局势紧张，越南武器进口仍减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-arms-imports-drop-trickle-despite-regional-tensions-2024-03-14/</link><description>周一公布的数据显示，越南去年的武器进口放缓，因为越南致力于将供应多样化，远离俄罗斯，而专家警告说，该国在地区冲突中可能很脆弱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-arms-imports-drop-trickle-despite-regional-tensions-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国炸鸡店爆炸造成7人死亡27人受伤调查开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/probe-begins-after-7-killed-27-injured-fried-chicken-shop-explosion-china-2024-03-14/</link><description>北京附近的中国三河县当地政府官员周四表示，他们已开始调查一家炸鸡店发生大规模爆炸的原因，爆炸造成 7 人死亡、27 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/probe-begins-after-7-killed-27-injured-fried-chicken-shop-explosion-china-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国库存数据和俄罗斯炼油厂遇袭支撑油价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-underpinned-by-us-inventory-data-attacks-russian-refineries-2024-03-14/</link><description>周四亚洲油价小幅上涨，受到美国强劲需求的支撑，此前汽油库存触及三个月低点，原油库存意外下降，乌克兰袭击俄罗斯炼油厂后供应担忧依然存在。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 01:51:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-underpinned-by-us-inventory-data-attacks-russian-refineries-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾和中国在敏感岛屿附近翻船后启动救援行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-dispatch-teams-join-boat-rescue-mission-near-sensitive-taiwan-2024-03-14/</link><description>由于敏感的台湾海峡紧张局势加剧，一艘渔船在台湾控制的金门群岛附近倾覆，台湾周四应中国要求派遣海岸警卫队船只参加救援任务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 01:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-dispatch-teams-join-boat-rescue-mission-near-sensitive-taiwan-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员表示，美韩防务谈判已步入正轨，但 11 月并非硬性最后期限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</link><description>拜登政府一位高级官员告诉路透社，美韩关于分担驻韩美军费用的谈判正在按计划进行，并且提前完成，但美方不一定会在 11 月美国大选之前看到一个严格的最后期限。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着关系改善，中国外交部长将于下周访问澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞周四表示，中国最高外交官、外交部长王毅将于下周访问澳大利亚，这是两国关系在多年紧张关系后进一步解冻的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>由于价格下跌打击高成本矿商，中国锂热潮放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</link><description>锂是电动汽车电池的关键原材料，其价格暴跌正在拖累中国的超轻金属开采，加上成本高昂的提取工艺，促使人们重新评估产量增长和新项目计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>保险公司友邦保险 (AIA) 2023 年新业务价值因香港销售强劲而飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</link><description>周四，友邦保险集团报告称，由于受益于香港对其保险产品的强劲需求，该公司的年度新业务价值 (VONB) 增长了 33%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着南海紧张局势升级，菲律宾马科斯将于下周会见布林肯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</link><description>马尼拉领导人办公室周三晚间在一份声明中表示，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯将于 3 月 19 日会见美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯，讨论合作和安全问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>